lead_paragraph: Taylor Force, an Army combat veteran and Vanderbilt graduate student, was killed by a Palestinian man who attacked groups of people in Jaffa.

byline.contributor: Eli Rosenberg contributed reporting from New York.

headline.print_headline: Student From U.S. Killed in Attacks Near Tel Aviv
headline.main: American Graduate Student Killed in Stabbing Rampage Near Tel Aviv

snippet: Taylor Force, an Army combat veteran and Vanderbilt graduate student, was killed by a Palestinian man who attacked groups of people in Jaffa.
abstract: Palestinian identified as Bashar Masalha carries out stabbing rampage and kills American student Taylor Force on coast near Tel Aviv; attack comes during visit by Vice Pres Joe Biden and in midst of trip by Vanderbilt University  graduate students.
